title: REPORT ON RESOLUTION PROVIDING FOR CONSIDERATION OF H.R. 3922,  COMMUNITY HEALTH AND MEDICAL PROFESSIONALS IMPROVE OUR NATION ACT OF

content.text:
2017

  Mr. BURGESS, from the Committee on Rules, submitted a privileged 
report (Rept. No. 115-382) on the resolution (H. Res. 601) providing 
for consideration of the bill (H.R. 3922) to extend funding for certain 
public health programs, and for other purposes, which was referred to 
the House Calendar and ordered to be printed.
content.speaker: Unknown
